text: Sharbat Ali Changezi (Urdu: ) is a Pakistani, Hazara retired Air Marshal. Changezi was born in Quetta, British India into a family of Hazara ethnic group, He was the Air Marshal of Pakistan Air Force and veteran of Indo- Pakistani War of 1965 and 1971. == Related pages == * Muhammad Musa Khan Hazara == References == == Other websites == * Category:Hazara people Category:Pakistani military people Category:1932 births Category:Quetta
